BUG-04: "Agree to Terms" Not Required

Severity: Medium

Environment: Windows 11, Chrome Browser

Steps to Reproduce (STR):

1)Navigate to the "Sign-up & Profile Wizard."

2)Fill all fields correctly but leave the "I agree to the Terms" box unchecked.

3)Click "Next."

Expected Result: The form should not proceed and should prompt the user to agree to the terms.

Actual Result: The form proceeds to the "Review" stage.

Evidence:
 ![Screenshot showing terms and condition not required](evidence\bug-04-terms-check.png)